Package Model

Class Taxi

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Taxi
  • public class Taxi
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represent taxi with its attributes, for example its descriptive elements; number plate. Also, logics attributes for example availability.

    • Constructor Detail

      • Taxi

        public Taxi​(java.lang.String numberPlate,
            java.lang.String carModel,
            java.lang.String carColor,
            int capacity,
            Driver driver)
        This is a constructor class of Taxi, we suppose the taxi is available when initialized.

        This class have param availability. availability contain info about if the car is available (Not receive in constructor, but setter in true)

        Parameters:
        numberPlate - Identifier of car.
        carModel - Specification of car design.
        carColor - Car primary color, that may change.
        capacity - How many people enter.
